00:19.561 --> 00:22.230
Times Square
was sex, sex, sex everywhere.

00:24.190 --> 00:26.401
There were men everywhere

00:27.986 --> 00:29.571
seeking what they were seeking.

00:33.116 --> 00:36.161
It wasn't just one or two girls
standing on a street corner.

00:38.747 --> 00:40.665
There were girls everywhere…

00:43.543 --> 00:46.713
and I was one of them for 13 years.

00:53.720 --> 00:58.016
One night I was out there,
and, uh, I had gotten into this car.

00:59.934 --> 01:03.063
This guy,
he was just some younger white guy.

01:03.938 --> 01:06.399
-I mean, normal-looking person.

01:06.483 --> 01:08.735
He didn't look, you know,
deranged or anything.

01:08.818 --> 01:10.737
And, um…
when I got in the car,

01:10.820 --> 01:13.948
I told this man to drive and take a left.

01:16.326 --> 01:18.661
And he didn't. He took a right.

01:21.122 --> 01:25.502
So he took me down to some…
by the river somewhere.

01:27.253 --> 01:28.296
And he had a gun.

01:29.130 --> 01:32.467
My heart just sank 'cause I knew…
I knew what was gonna happen.

01:32.550 --> 01:35.762
-When someone thinks they've bought you,

01:35.845 --> 01:38.640
they think they could
do whatever they want to with you.

01:41.017 --> 01:43.478
And he did rape me, and he did rob me.

01:47.107 --> 01:50.985
And then he told me, "Get out of the car,
and don't turn around."

01:55.949 --> 01:59.119
And I… I didn't. I got out of the car,
and I didn't turn around.

02:01.704 --> 02:04.165
I thought he was still
gonna shoot me in the back.

02:06.876 --> 02:10.505
I know my mind
kind of left my body during that.

02:16.427 --> 02:17.554
It was horrible.

02:17.637 --> 02:21.141
It's beyond horrible.
There's no word to describe it.

02:25.770 --> 02:29.732
I'm pretty sure that I was
in the car with a serial killer,

02:31.442 --> 02:33.403
and I don't know why he didn't kill me.

02:35.321 --> 02:36.197
