42:18.911 --> 42:23.123
This individual
had asked her to come with him,

42:24.083 --> 42:25.084
and she did.

42:28.504 --> 42:32.091
At a bar,
he came across very friendly,

42:32.174 --> 42:33.801
and he said his name was Tommy.

42:35.386 --> 42:37.721
He, uh, bought her drinks.

42:39.181 --> 42:41.100
He showed interest in her.

42:42.017 --> 42:44.144
She said she wanted
to get away from the pimp.

42:44.228 --> 42:47.273
He said, "I can help you out.
I'll give you money. You can go home."

42:47.356 --> 42:49.650
"I'm gonna help
you out of your situation."

42:49.733 --> 42:53.279
He promised her if he…
if she did go with him

42:53.362 --> 42:58.701
that he would get her safely
to a bus station in New Jersey

42:58.784 --> 43:02.413
so that she could make her escape,
uh, from her pimp.

43:04.206 --> 43:06.625
She felt very comfortable
with this man.

43:07.376 --> 43:09.128
She trusted him,

43:09.211 --> 43:12.590
so she got in the car with him willingly

43:13.716 --> 43:15.342
and drove to New Jersey.

43:18.679 --> 43:20.180
And then he said,

43:20.264 --> 43:22.308
"I'd like to have sex
with you before you go,"

43:22.391 --> 43:25.686
and he took her to the Quality Inn motel.

43:35.404 --> 43:37.906
He wanted to put her in handcuffs,

43:39.700 --> 43:41.744
that he wanted to spank her.

43:43.412 --> 43:45.372
That's when the horror began.

43:46.040 --> 43:48.125
Next thing you know, he's attacking her.

43:48.709 --> 43:51.837
She was beaten, tortured,

43:51.920 --> 43:53.839
sexually assaulted,

43:55.424 --> 43:57.926
on and on for hours.

44:09.438 --> 44:13.359
And finally,
he removed the handcuffs…

44:16.528 --> 44:18.322
…and pointed a gun at her.

44:24.119 --> 44:26.038
She knew she had to get out.

44:32.503 --> 44:35.214
She grabs the pistol, points it at him…

44:37.299 --> 44:38.550
pulls the trigger.

44:41.387 --> 44:43.097
The trigger goes "click."

44:45.724 --> 44:48.310
It's not a real pistol.
It's a fake pistol.

44:48.894 --> 44:51.438
-Now he's coming at her with a knife.

44:51.522 --> 44:54.733
