is already frightened and horrified

44:58.737 --> 45:01.865
by the earlier homicide
of Valerie Ann Street.

45:03.325 --> 45:06.412
-They send somebody to the door.

45:06.495 --> 45:08.580
And they said, "Is everything all right?"

45:09.415 --> 45:11.375
Leslie went to the door…

45:12.584 --> 45:16.046
…and he warned her
to tell them that she was okay.

45:18.340 --> 45:22.386
She managed to get the door open
just a… a wee bit enough

45:23.470 --> 45:26.473
to make some kind of a hand signal.
